name: OtterBox Tie Down Kit
description: Keep you cooler anchored and upright when things get rough. This tie-down kit includes straps to secure your OtterBox Venture cooler –  perfect for times when from A-to-B gets a little rocky.Burly zinc non-slip buckles keep your cooler anchored.Includes 2 x 182cm (6ft.) tie-down straps.Straps have a 952kg (2100lb.) breaking strength and 317kg (700lb.) working load.Works with all Venture coolers.Covered by OtterBox’s limited lifetime warranty.
